FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Brands] AS [b] ON [p].[BrandId] = [b].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p1].[Id], [p1].[ColorId], [p1].[CreatedDate], [p1].[ProductId], [c0].[Id] AS [Id0], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c0].[Name]
    FROM [ProductColors] AS [p1]
    INNER JOIN [Colors] AS [c0] ON [p1].[ColorId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p2].[Id], [p2].[CreatedDate], [p2].[ProductId], [p2].[TagId], [t1].[Id] AS [Id0], [t1].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [t1].[Name]
    FROM [ProductTags] AS [p2]
    INNER JOIN [Tags] AS [t1] ON [p2].[TagId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [p].[Id] = [t0].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [b].[Id], [p0].[Id], [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t0].[Id]

SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[BrandId], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[Stock], [c].[Id], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[Image], [c].[Name], [b].[Id], [b].[CreatedDate], [b].[Image], [b].[Name], [p0].[Id], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Img], [p0].[IsMain], [p0].[ProductId], [t].[Id], [t].[ColorId], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Id0], [t].[CreatedDate0], [t].[Name], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[ProductId], [t0].[TagId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Brands] AS [b] ON [p].[BrandId] = [b].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p1].[Id], [p1].[ColorId], [p1].[CreatedDate], [p1].[ProductId], [c0].[Id] AS [Id0], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c0].[Name]
    FROM [ProductColors] AS [p1]
    INNER JOIN [Colors] AS [c0] ON [p1].[ColorId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p2].[Id], [p2].[CreatedDate], [p2].[ProductId], [p2].[TagId], [t1].[Id] AS [Id0], [t1].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [t1].[Name]
    FROM [ProductTags] AS [p2]
    INNER JOIN [Tags] AS [t1] ON [p2].[TagId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [p].[Id] = [t0].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [b].[Id], [p0].[Id], [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t0].[Id]

    SELECT [p1].[Id], [p1].[ColorId], [p1].[CreatedDate], [p1].[ProductId], [c0].[Id] AS [Id0], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c0].[Name]
    FROM [ProductColors] AS [p1]

) AS [t0] ON [p].[Id] = [t0].[ProductId]

) AS [t0] ON [p].[Id] = [t0].[ProductId]

SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[BrandId], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[Stock], [c].[Id], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[Image], [c].[Name], [b].[Id], [b].[CreatedDate], [b].[Image], [b].[Name], [p0].[Id], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Img], [p0].[IsMain], [p0].[ProductId], [t].[Id], [t].[ColorId], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Id0], [t].[CreatedDate0], [t].[Name], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[ProductId], [t0].[TagId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Brands] AS [b] ON [p].[BrandId] = [b].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p1].[Id], [p1].[ColorId], [p1].[CreatedDate], [p1].[ProductId], [c0].[Id] AS [Id0], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c0].[Name]
    FROM [ProductColors] AS [p1]
    INNER JOIN [Colors] AS [c0] ON [p1].[ColorId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p2].[Id], [p2].[CreatedDate], [p2].[ProductId], [p2].[TagId], [t1].[Id] AS [Id0], [t1].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [t1].[Name]
    FROM [ProductTags] AS [p2]

) AS [t0] ON [p].[Id] = [t0].[ProductId]
WHERE LTRIM(RTRIM(LOWER([p].[Name]))) LIKE @__Trim_0_contains ESCAPE N'\' OR LTRIM(RTRIM(LOWER([c].[Name]))) LIKE @__Trim_0_contains ESCAPE N'\'

INNER JOIN [Brands] AS [b] ON [p].[BrandId] = [b].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]

FROM [Products] AS [p]

INNER JOIN [Brands] AS [b] ON [p].[BrandId] = [b].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p1].[Id], [p1].[ColorId], [p1].[CreatedDate], [p1].[ProductId], [c0].[Id] AS [Id0], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c0].[Name]
    FROM [ProductColors] AS [p1]
    INNER JOIN [Colors] AS [c0] ON [p1].[ColorId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]

    SELECT [p2].[Id], [p2].[CreatedDate], [p2].[ProductId], [p2].[TagId], [t1].[Id] AS [Id0], [t1].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [t1].[Name]

    INNER JOIN [Tags] AS [t1] ON [p2].[TagId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [p].[Id] = [t0].[ProductId]

LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]

) AS [t0] ON [p].[Id] = [t0].[ProductId]

SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[BrandId], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[Stock], [c].[Id], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[Image], [c].[Name], [b].[Id], [b].[CreatedDate], [b].[Image], [b].[Name], [p0].[Id], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Img], [p0].[IsMain], [p0].[ProductId], [t].[Id], [t].[ColorId], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Id0], [t].[CreatedDate0], [t].[Name], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[ProductId], [t0].[TagId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Brands] AS [b] ON [p].[BrandId] = [b].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p1].[Id], [p1].[ColorId], [p1].[CreatedDate], [p1].[ProductId], [c0].[Id] AS [Id0], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c0].[Name]
    FROM [ProductColors] AS [p1]
    INNER JOIN [Colors] AS [c0] ON [p1].[ColorId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p2].[Id], [p2].[CreatedDate], [p2].[ProductId], [p2].[TagId], [t1].[Id] AS [Id0], [t1].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [t1].[Name]
    FROM [ProductTags] AS [p2]
    INNER JOIN [Tags] AS [t1] ON [p2].[TagId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [p].[Id] = [t0].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [b].[Id], [p0].[Id], [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t0].[Id]

FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Brands] AS [b] ON [p].[BrandId] = [b].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p1].[Id], [p1].[ColorId], [p1].[CreatedDate], [p1].[ProductId], [c0].[Id] AS [Id0], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c0].[Name]

) AS [t0] ON [p].[Id] = [t0].[ProductId]

FROM (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[BrandId], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[Stock]

    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [t].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Brands] AS [b] ON [t].[BrandId] = [b].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [t].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p1].[Id], [p1].[ColorId], [p1].[CreatedDate], [p1].[ProductId], [c0].[Id] AS [Id0], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c0].[Name]

    FROM [ProductTags] AS [p2]
    INNER JOIN [Tags] AS [t2] ON [p2].[TagId] = [t2].[Id]
) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [c].[Id], [b].[Id], [p0].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t1].[Id]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[BrandId], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[Description], [t].[Name], [t].[Price], [t].[Stock], [c].[Id], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[Image], [c].[Name], [b].[Id], [b].[CreatedDate], [b].[Image], [b].[Name], [p0].[Id], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Img], [p0].[IsMain], [p0].[ProductId], [t0].[Id], [t0].[ColorId], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[ProductId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name], [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[ProductId], [t1].[TagId], [t1].[Id0], [t1].[CreatedDate0], [t1].[Name]
FROM (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[BrandId], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[Stock]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [t].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Brands] AS [b] ON [t].[BrandId] = [b].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [t].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p1].[Id], [p1].[ColorId], [p1].[CreatedDate], [p1].[ProductId], [c0].[Id] AS [Id0], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c0].[Name]
    FROM [ProductColors] AS [p1]
    INNER JOIN [Colors] AS [c0] ON [p1].[ColorId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p2].[Id], [p2].[CreatedDate], [p2].[ProductId], [p2].[TagId], [t2].[Id] AS [Id0], [t2].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [t2].[Name]
    FROM [ProductTags] AS [p2]
    INNER JOIN [Tags] AS [t2] ON [p2].[TagId] = [t2].[Id]
) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [c].[Id], [b].[Id], [p0].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t1].[Id]

INNER JOIN [Brands] AS [b] ON [t].[BrandId] = [b].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [t].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p1].[Id], [p1].[ColorId], [p1].[CreatedDate], [p1].[ProductId], [c0].[Id] AS [Id0], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c0].[Name]
    FROM [ProductColors] AS [p1]
    INNER JOIN [Colors] AS [c0] ON [p1].[ColorId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p2].[Id], [p2].[CreatedDate], [p2].[ProductId], [p2].[TagId], [t2].[Id] AS [Id0], [t2].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [t2].[Name]
    FROM [ProductTags] AS [p2]
    INNER JOIN [Tags] AS [t2] ON [p2].[TagId] = [t2].[Id]
) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [c].[Id], [b].[Id], [p0].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t1].[Id]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[BrandId], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[Description], [t].[Name], [t].[Price], [t].[Stock], [c].[Id], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[Image], [c].[Name], [b].[Id], [b].[CreatedDate], [b].[Image], [b].[Name], [p0].[Id], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Img], [p0].[IsMain], [p0].[ProductId], [t0].[Id], [t0].[ColorId], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[ProductId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name], [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[ProductId], [t1].[TagId], [t1].[Id0], [t1].[CreatedDate0], [t1].[Name]
FROM (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[BrandId], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[Stock]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [t].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Brands] AS [b] ON [t].[BrandId] = [b].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [t].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p1].[Id], [p1].[ColorId], [p1].[CreatedDate], [p1].[ProductId], [c0].[Id] AS [Id0], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c0].[Name]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductId]

    FROM [ProductTags] AS [p2]
    INNER JOIN [Tags] AS [t2] ON [p2].[TagId] = [t2].[Id]
) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[ProductId]

    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[BrandId], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[Stock]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [t].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Brands] AS [b] ON [t].[BrandId] = [b].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [t].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]

) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[ProductId]

FROM (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[BrandId], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[Stock]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [t].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Brands] AS [b] ON [t].[BrandId] = [b].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [t].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]

    SELECT [p1].[Id], [p1].[ColorId], [p1].[CreatedDate], [p1].[ProductId], [c0].[Id] AS [Id0], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c0].[Name]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductId]

    FROM [ProductTags] AS [p2]
    INNER JOIN [Tags] AS [t2] ON [p2].[TagId] = [t2].[Id]
) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[ProductId]

FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Brands] AS [b] ON [p].[BrandId] = [b].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p1].[Id], [p1].[ColorId], [p1].[CreatedDate], [p1].[ProductId], [c0].[Id] AS [Id0], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c0].[Name]
    FROM [ProductColors] AS [p1]
    INNER JOIN [Colors] AS [c0] ON [p1].[ColorId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]

) AS [t0] ON [p].[Id] = [t0].[ProductId]

    SELECT [p1].[Id], [p1].[ColorId], [p1].[CreatedDate], [p1].[ProductId], [c0].[Id] AS [Id0], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c0].[Name]
    FROM [ProductColors] AS [p1]
    INNER JOIN [Colors] AS [c0] ON [p1].[ColorId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p2].[Id], [p2].[CreatedDate], [p2].[ProductId], [p2].[TagId], [t1].[Id] AS [Id0], [t1].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [t1].[Name]
    FROM [ProductTags] AS [p2]
    INNER JOIN [Tags] AS [t1] ON [p2].[TagId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [p].[Id] = [t0].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [b].[Id], [p0].[Id], [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t0].[Id]

SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[BrandId], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[Stock], [c].[Id], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[Image], [c].[Name], [b].[Id], [b].[CreatedDate], [b].[Image], [b].[Name], [p0].[Id], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Img], [p0].[IsMain], [p0].[ProductId], [t].[Id], [t].[ColorId], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Id0], [t].[CreatedDate0], [t].[Name], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[ProductId], [t0].[TagId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Brands] AS [b] ON [p].[BrandId] = [b].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p1].[Id], [p1].[ColorId], [p1].[CreatedDate], [p1].[ProductId], [c0].[Id] AS [Id0], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c0].[Name]
    FROM [ProductColors] AS [p1]
    INNER JOIN [Colors] AS [c0] ON [p1].[ColorId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p2].[Id], [p2].[CreatedDate], [p2].[ProductId], [p2].[TagId], [t1].[Id] AS [Id0], [t1].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [t1].[Name]
    FROM [ProductTags] AS [p2]
    INNER JOIN [Tags] AS [t1] ON [p2].[TagId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [p].[Id] = [t0].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [b].[Id], [p0].[Id], [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t0].[Id]

SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[BrandId], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[Stock], [c].[Id], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[Image], [c].[Name], [b].[Id], [b].[CreatedDate], [b].[Image], [b].[Name], [p0].[Id], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Img], [p0].[IsMain], [p0].[ProductId], [t].[Id], [t].[ColorId], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Id0], [t].[CreatedDate0], [t].[Name], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[ProductId], [t0].[TagId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Brands] AS [b] ON [p].[BrandId] = [b].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p1].[Id], [p1].[ColorId], [p1].[CreatedDate], [p1].[ProductId], [c0].[Id] AS [Id0], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c0].[Name]
    FROM [ProductColors] AS [p1]
    INNER JOIN [Colors] AS [c0] ON [p1].[ColorId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p2].[Id], [p2].[CreatedDate], [p2].[ProductId], [p2].[TagId], [t1].[Id] AS [Id0], [t1].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [t1].[Name]
    FROM [ProductTags] AS [p2]
    INNER JOIN [Tags] AS [t1] ON [p2].[TagId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [p].[Id] = [t0].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [b].[Id], [p0].[Id], [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t0].[Id]

SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[BrandId], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[Stock], [c].[Id], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[Image], [c].[Name], [b].[Id], [b].[CreatedDate], [b].[Image], [b].[Name], [p0].[Id], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Img], [p0].[IsMain], [p0].[ProductId], [t].[Id], [t].[ColorId], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Id0], [t].[CreatedDate0], [t].[Name], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[ProductId], [t0].[TagId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Brands] AS [b] ON [p].[BrandId] = [b].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p1].[Id], [p1].[ColorId], [p1].[CreatedDate], [p1].[ProductId], [c0].[Id] AS [Id0], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c0].[Name]
    FROM [ProductColors] AS [p1]
    INNER JOIN [Colors] AS [c0] ON [p1].[ColorId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p2].[Id], [p2].[CreatedDate], [p2].[ProductId], [p2].[TagId], [t1].[Id] AS [Id0], [t1].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [t1].[Name]
    FROM [ProductTags] AS [p2]
    INNER JOIN [Tags] AS [t1] ON [p2].[TagId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [p].[Id] = [t0].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [b].[Id], [p0].[Id], [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t0].[Id]

FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Brands] AS [b] ON [p].[BrandId] = [b].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p1].[Id], [p1].[ColorId], [p1].[CreatedDate], [p1].[ProductId], [c0].[Id] AS [Id0], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c0].[Name]
    FROM [ProductColors] AS [p1]
    INNER JOIN [Colors] AS [c0] ON [p1].[ColorId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]

) AS [t0] ON [p].[Id] = [t0].[ProductId]

SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[BrandId], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[Stock], [c].[Id], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[Image], [c].[Name], [b].[Id], [b].[CreatedDate], [b].[Image], [b].[Name], [p0].[Id], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Img], [p0].[IsMain], [p0].[ProductId], [t].[Id], [t].[ColorId], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Id0], [t].[CreatedDate0], [t].[Name], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[ProductId], [t0].[TagId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Brands] AS [b] ON [p].[BrandId] = [b].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p1].[Id], [p1].[ColorId], [p1].[CreatedDate], [p1].[ProductId], [c0].[Id] AS [Id0], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c0].[Name]
    FROM [ProductColors] AS [p1]
    INNER JOIN [Colors] AS [c0] ON [p1].[ColorId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p2].[Id], [p2].[CreatedDate], [p2].[ProductId], [p2].[TagId], [t1].[Id] AS [Id0], [t1].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [t1].[Name]
    FROM [ProductTags] AS [p2]
    INNER JOIN [Tags] AS [t1] ON [p2].[TagId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [p].[Id] = [t0].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [b].[Id], [p0].[Id], [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t0].[Id]

FROM [Products] AS [p]

INNER JOIN [Brands] AS [b] ON [p].[BrandId] = [b].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p1].[Id], [p1].[ColorId], [p1].[CreatedDate], [p1].[ProductId], [c0].[Id] AS [Id0], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c0].[Name]
    FROM [ProductColors] AS [p1]

) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]

) AS [t0] ON [p].[Id] = [t0].[ProductId]

FROM (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[BrandId], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[Stock]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [t].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Brands] AS [b] ON [t].[BrandId] = [b].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [t].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p1].[Id], [p1].[ColorId], [p1].[CreatedDate], [p1].[ProductId], [c0].[Id] AS [Id0], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c0].[Name]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductId]

    FROM [ProductTags] AS [p2]
    INNER JOIN [Tags] AS [t2] ON [p2].[TagId] = [t2].[Id]
) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [c].[Id], [b].[Id], [p0].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t1].[Id]

SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[BrandId], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[Stock], [c].[Id], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[Image], [c].[Name], [b].[Id], [b].[CreatedDate], [b].[Image], [b].[Name], [p0].[Id], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Img], [p0].[IsMain], [p0].[ProductId], [t].[Id], [t].[ColorId], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Id0], [t].[CreatedDate0], [t].[Name], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[ProductId], [t0].[TagId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Brands] AS [b] ON [p].[BrandId] = [b].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p1].[Id], [p1].[ColorId], [p1].[CreatedDate], [p1].[ProductId], [c0].[Id] AS [Id0], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c0].[Name]
    FROM [ProductColors] AS [p1]
    INNER JOIN [Colors] AS [c0] ON [p1].[ColorId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p2].[Id], [p2].[CreatedDate], [p2].[ProductId], [p2].[TagId], [t1].[Id] AS [Id0], [t1].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [t1].[Name]
    FROM [ProductTags] AS [p2]
    INNER JOIN [Tags] AS [t1] ON [p2].[TagId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [p].[Id] = [t0].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [b].[Id], [p0].[Id], [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t0].[Id]

SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[BrandId], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[Stock], [c].[Id], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[Image], [c].[Name], [b].[Id], [b].[CreatedDate], [b].[Image], [b].[Name], [p0].[Id], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Img], [p0].[IsMain], [p0].[ProductId], [t].[Id], [t].[ColorId], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Id0], [t].[CreatedDate0], [t].[Name], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[ProductId], [t0].[TagId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Brands] AS [b] ON [p].[BrandId] = [b].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p1].[Id], [p1].[ColorId], [p1].[CreatedDate], [p1].[ProductId], [c0].[Id] AS [Id0], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c0].[Name]
    FROM [ProductColors] AS [p1]
    INNER JOIN [Colors] AS [c0] ON [p1].[ColorId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p2].[Id], [p2].[CreatedDate], [p2].[ProductId], [p2].[TagId], [t1].[Id] AS [Id0], [t1].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [t1].[Name]
    FROM [ProductTags] AS [p2]
    INNER JOIN [Tags] AS [t1] ON [p2].[TagId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [p].[Id] = [t0].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [b].[Id], [p0].[Id], [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t0].[Id]

FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Brands] AS [b] ON [p].[BrandId] = [b].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p1].[Id], [p1].[ColorId], [p1].[CreatedDate], [p1].[ProductId], [c0].[Id] AS [Id0], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c0].[Name]
    FROM [ProductColors] AS [p1]
    INNER JOIN [Colors] AS [c0] ON [p1].[ColorId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]

    SELECT [p2].[Id], [p2].[CreatedDate], [p2].[ProductId], [p2].[TagId], [t1].[Id] AS [Id0], [t1].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [t1].[Name]
    FROM [ProductTags] AS [p2]
    INNER JOIN [Tags] AS [t1] ON [p2].[TagId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [p].[Id] = [t0].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [b].[Id], [p0].[Id], [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t0].[Id]

FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Brands] AS [b] ON [p].[BrandId] = [b].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p1].[Id], [p1].[ColorId], [p1].[CreatedDate], [p1].[ProductId], [c0].[Id] AS [Id0], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c0].[Name]
    FROM [ProductColors] AS [p1]

) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]

) AS [t0] ON [p].[Id] = [t0].[ProductId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[BrandId], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[Description], [t].[Name], [t].[Price], [t].[Stock], [c].[Id], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[Image], [c].[Name], [b].[Id], [b].[CreatedDate], [b].[Image], [b].[Name], [t0].[Id], [t0].[ColorId], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[ProductId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name], [p1].[Id], [p1].[CreatedDate], [p1].[Img], [p1].[IsMain], [p1].[ProductId]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_1) [p].[Id], [p].[BrandId], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[Stock], NEWID() AS [c]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    WHERE [p].[CategoryId] = @__categoryId_0
    ORDER BY NEWID()
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [t].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Brands] AS [b] ON [t].[BrandId] = [b].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p0].[Id], [p0].[ColorId], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[ProductId], [c0].[Id] AS [Id0], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c0].[Name]
    FROM [ProductColors] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN [Colors] AS [c0] ON [p0].[ColorId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p1] ON [t].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [t].[c], [t].[Id], [c].[Id], [b].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0]

    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[BrandId], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[Stock]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]

) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[ProductId]

    SELECT TOP(1) [p].[Id], [p].[BrandId], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[Stock], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Image], [c].[Name] AS [Name0], [b].[Id] AS [Id1], [b].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [b].[Image] AS [Image0], [b].[Name] AS [Name1]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Brands] AS [b] ON [p].[BrandId] = [b].[Id]
    WHERE [p].[Id] = @__selectedProductId_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p0].[Id], [p0].[ColorId], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[ProductId], [c0].[Id] AS [Id0], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c0].[Name]
    FROM [ProductColors] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN [Colors] AS [c0] ON [p0].[ColorId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p1] ON [t].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0]

SELECT TOP(@__p_2) [p].[Id], [p].[BrandId], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[Stock]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
WHERE [p].[CategoryId] = @__categoryId_0 AND [p].[Id] <> @__selectedProductId_1
ORDER BY NEWID()

SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[BrandId], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[Stock], [c].[Id], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[Image], [c].[Name], [b].[Id], [b].[CreatedDate], [b].[Image], [b].[Name], [p0].[Id], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Img], [p0].[IsMain], [p0].[ProductId], [t].[Id], [t].[ColorId], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Id0], [t].[CreatedDate0], [t].[Name], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[ProductId], [t0].[TagId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Brands] AS [b] ON [p].[BrandId] = [b].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (

SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[BrandId], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[Stock], [c].[Id], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[Image], [c].[Name], [b].[Id], [b].[CreatedDate], [b].[Image], [b].[Name], [p0].[Id], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Img], [p0].[IsMain], [p0].[ProductId], [t].[Id], [t].[ColorId], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Id0], [t].[CreatedDate0], [t].[Name], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[ProductId], [t0].[TagId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Brands] AS [b] ON [p].[BrandId] = [b].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p1].[Id], [p1].[ColorId], [p1].[CreatedDate], [p1].[ProductId], [c0].[Id] AS [Id0], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c0].[Name]
    FROM [ProductColors] AS [p1]
    INNER JOIN [Colors] AS [c0] ON [p1].[ColorId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p2].[Id], [p2].[CreatedDate], [p2].[ProductId], [p2].[TagId], [t1].[Id] AS [Id0], [t1].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [t1].[Name]
    FROM [ProductTags] AS [p2]
    INNER JOIN [Tags] AS [t1] ON [p2].[TagId] = [t1].[Id]

SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[BrandId], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[Stock], [c].[Id], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[Image], [c].[Name], [b].[Id], [b].[CreatedDate], [b].[Image], [b].[Name], [p0].[Id], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[Img], [p0].[IsMain], [p0].[ProductId], [t].[Id], [t].[ColorId], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[ProductId], [t].[Id0], [t].[CreatedDate0], [t].[Name], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[ProductId], [t0].[TagId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Brands] AS [b] ON [p].[BrandId] = [b].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [p].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p1].[Id], [p1].[ColorId], [p1].[CreatedDate], [p1].[ProductId], [c0].[Id] AS [Id0], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c0].[Name]
    FROM [ProductColors] AS [p1]
    INNER JOIN [Colors] AS [c0] ON [p1].[ColorId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [p].[Id] = [t].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p2].[Id], [p2].[CreatedDate], [p2].[ProductId], [p2].[TagId], [t1].[Id] AS [Id0], [t1].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [t1].[Name]
    FROM [ProductTags] AS [p2]
    INNER JOIN [Tags] AS [t1] ON [p2].[TagId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [p].[Id] = [t0].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [p].[Id], [c].[Id], [b].[Id], [p0].[Id], [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t0].[Id]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [p].[Id], [p].[BrandId], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Description], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[Stock], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Image], [c].[Name] AS [Name0], [b].[Id] AS [Id1], [b].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [b].[Image] AS [Image0], [b].[Name] AS [Name1]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Brands] AS [b] ON [p].[BrandId] = [b].[Id]
    WHERE [p].[Id] = @__selectedProductId_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p0].[Id], [p0].[ColorId], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[ProductId], [c0].[Id] AS [Id0], [c0].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c0].[Name]
    FROM [ProductColors] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN [Colors] AS [c0] ON [p0].[ColorId] = [c0].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p1] ON [t].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0]
